Greg Perry is University Minister at Grace Valley Christian Center which has been the subject of considerable Grace Valley Christian Center/Allegations controversy.  He is active with the campus ministry Grace Alive as well as with the international ministry http://www.gracevalley.org/globalgrace/index.html Global Grace.  He spoke at http://www.youtube.com/watch?vmsIAEGWr9Rw&featurerelated Bryn Ransdells memorial.
